name: After Doom ][
description: This is the first .WAD I've decided to try and distribute properly, although I have done others in the past and some are almost as good. (So read on knowing that this is not one of those ones with a severe case of Tutti-Fruity (There is a tiny amount or a case full of cybers) This is meant for Deathmatch V2.0, although single player is possible ... if you really want.
